    m_classes:
      m_baseClasses:
      - m_name: Scout
        m_description: Scouts are all about access and options. They freely move
          through the battlefield to gain the best vantage points to unleash their
          barrage of arrows. Their use of special ammo allows them to have a tactical
          edge in battle.
        m_primaryStats: 01000000
        m_abilities:
        - '(AUG) Ranged Finesse: +1 to attack rolls that are near or far.'
        - '(BON) Steady Draw: Unhindered by difficult terrain and double the effect
          of arrows.'
        - (AUG) Starts each combat with a Feather Arrow.
      m_crossClasses:
      - m_name: Thief
        m_description: A master of deceit and misdirection.
        m_primaryStats: 0100000005000000
        m_abilities:
        - (BON) Equip a weapon you've disarmed.
        - '(BON/ACT) One Up: Use a BON or ACT that another player used on their last
          turn. They can''t use that action for 1 turn. CHA DC 12.'
        - (AUG) Starts each combat with a Scatter Arrow.
        - +2 bonus to stealing checks
